"https://stomp.github.io/stomp-specification-1.2.html#Heart-beating[STOMP "
"heartbeats].  To configure a scheduler, you can declare your own "
"`TaskScheduler` bean and set it through the "
"`MessageBrokerRegistry`. Alternatively, you can use the one that is "
"automatically declared in the built-in WebSocket configuration, however, "
